children.query: SELECT 1 AS one FROM "users" WHERE LOWER("users"."email") = LOWER($1) LIMIT $2

rootActions.query: SELECT "flipper_features"."key" AS feature_key, "flipper_gates"."key", "flipper_gates"."value" FROM "flipper_features" LEFT OUTER JOIN "flipper_gates" ON "flipper_features"."key" = "flipper_gates"."feature_key"

children.query: SELECT "roles".* FROM "roles" INNER JOIN "users_roles" ON "roles"."id" = "users_roles"."role_id" WHERE "users_roles"."user_id" = $1 AND (((roles.name = 'suspended') AND (roles.resource_type IS NULL) AND (roles.resource_id IS NULL)))

SELECT "roles".* FROM "roles" INNER JOIN "users_roles" ON "roles"."id" = "users_roles"."role_id" WHERE "users_roles"."user_id" = $1 AND (((roles.name = 'suspended') AND (roles.resource_type IS NULL) AND (roles.resource_id IS NULL)))
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "articles" WHERE "articles"."user_id" = $1 AND "articles"."published" = $2 AND (published_at <= '2023-01-24 17:13:12.372258') AND (created_at > '2023-01-24 17:08:12.372363')
SELECT 1 AS one FROM "articles" WHERE "articles"."body_markdown" = $1 AND "articles"."user_id" = $2 AND "articles"."title" = $3 LIMIT $4
SELECT 1 AS one FROM "articles" WHERE "articles"."slug" = $1 AND "articles"."user_id" = $2 LIMIT $3
SELECT "tag_adjustments"."tag_name" FROM "tag_adjustments" WHERE "tag_adjustments"."article_id" IS NULL AND "tag_adjustments"."adjustment_type" = $1 AND "tag_adjustments"."status" = $2
SELECT "articles"."id" FROM "articles" WHERE "articles"."user_id" = $1 AND "articles"."published" = $2 AND (published_at <= '2023-01-24 17:13:12.420927') ORDER BY "articles"."published_at" ASC

SELECT "tags".* FROM "tags" INNER JOIN "taggings" ON "tags"."id" = "taggings"."tag_id" WHERE "taggings"."taggable_id" = $1 AND "taggings"."taggable_type" = $2 AND (taggings.context = 'tags' AND taggings.tagger_id IS NULL)
